**SECOND**

For responsive video you can use percentage for the width and make the height auto. Like so:

    #videofetch {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        border: 2px solid white; 
        width: 10%;
        height: auto;
    }

Or even you can use **max-width**. it will go smaller if the video is smaller but never go higher than 20%.

    #videofetch {
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        border: 2px solid white; 
        max-width: 20%;
        height: auto;
    }

